snippet.title: WireWay Trailer ( Nintendo DS)
snippet.description:
Introducing Wiley Springer the lovable and mischievous alien, whos trouble making has landed him in a big dilemma! With his newly acquired Èlan wire mining skills, he tries to obtain the Super Èlan, by battling alien gangs, avoiding obstacles and ultimately trying to defeat the alien boss, to bring back the spirit and love throughout the Universe!

Rated E (Comic Mischief)
Available Fall 2009
http://www.konami.com/wireway/
